detaileddescription.para:
This is a local variable used in function SysWDDiag_DTC000121() to implement the 0x000121 DTC functionality 

range The variable is of type uint16, matching the type of msgcount - the passed by reference parameter of the Spi2SysWD_getClientInfo(). 
 values Variable will take the value from the message counter parameter of Spi2SysWD_getClientInfo() external function. 
 unit Counter 
 context {LinTask/Diag_Chorus_RL78, SysWDDiag_DTC000121(), "Updated an read in the current module"} 
 protection {local, "This is a local variable in the scope of this module"}

This function will: 


correlate the DTC ID received as parameter (from the client) with the DTC ID defined in DEM; 

it will call the Dem_SetEventStatus function with the status received as parameter.
